\c 9
\s Vanhu, vakazogara Jerusaremu,
\s shure kwokutapwa kwavo
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo vaIsiraeri vose vakave rengwa mazita avo; tarirai, akanyorwa ose multuku yamadzimautho alsiraeri. VaJudha vakazotapwa, vakaiswa Bhabhironi nokuda kwokudarika kwavo.
\p
\v 2 Zvino, vakatanga kugara panyika yavo napamaguta avo, vakanga vari vaIsiraeri, navapirisiti, navaRevhi, navaNetinimi.
\v 3 PaJerusaremu ndipo pakanga pagere vana vaJudha, navana vaBhenjamini, navana vaEfuremu, navaManase;
\v 4 Utai mwanakomana waA m ihudhi, mwanakomana waOmiri, mwanakomana waImiri, mwanakomana waBhani, wavana vaPerezi mwanakomana waJudha.
\v 5 NavaShiro: Asaya mwanakomana wedangwe, navanakomana vake.
\v 6 Vanakomana vaZera: Jeueri, nehama dzavo, vana mazana rnatanhatu namakumi mapfurnbamwe.
\p
\v 7 Vanakomana vaBhenjamini: Saru, mwanakomana waMeshirami, mwanakomana waHodhavia, mwanakomana waHasenua.
\p
\v 8 Nalbheneya, mwanakomana waJehorami, naEra mwanakomana waUzi, mwanakomana waMikiri, naMeshurami mwanakomana waShefatia, mwanakomana waReueri, mwanakomana waIbhiniya;
\v 9 nehama dzavo, marudzi avo aisvika mazana mapfumbamwe namakumi mashanu namatanhatu. Varume ava vose vakanga vari vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba padzimba dzamadzibaba avo.
\p
\v 10 Vavapristi: Jedheiya, naJehoyaribhi, naJakini;
\v 11 naAzaria, mwanakomana waHirikia, mwanakomana waMeshurami, mwanakomana waZadhoki, mwanakomana waMerayoti, mwanakomana waAhitubhi, mukuru paimba yaMwari,
\v 12 naAdhaya, mwanakomana waJehorami, mwanakomana waPashuri, mwanakomana waMarikija, naMaasai, mwanakomana waAdhieri, mwanakomana waJazera, mwanakomana waMeshurami, mwanakomana waMeshiremiti, mwanakomana waImeri;
\v 13 nehama dzavo, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avo vakasvika chiuru chimwe namazana manomwe namakumi matanhatu; varume vane simba kwazvo noumhare pabasa rokushumira paimba yaMwari.
\p
\v 14 VavaRevhi: Shemaya mwanakomana waHashubhi, mwanakomana waAzirikami, mwanakomana waHashabhia, wavanakomana vaMerari;
\v 15 naBhakibhakari, naHoreshi, naGarari, naMatania mwanakomma waMika, vtim arakoman.a waZikiri, mwanakomana waAsafi;
\v 16 naObhadhiya mwanakomana waShemaya, mwanakomana waGarari, mwanakomana waAsa, mwanakomana waErikana, vakanga vagere pamisha yavaNetofati.
\p
\v 17 Vatariri vamasuo: Sharumi, naAkubhi, naTarimoni, naAhikami, nehama dzavo; Sharumi ndiye akanga ari mukuru;
\v 18 ndivo vaitarira suo ramambo rokumabvazuva kusvikira zvino; vakanga vari vatariri vamasuo emisasa yavana vaRevhi.
\p
\v 19 Sharumi mwanakomana waKore, mwanakomana waEbhiasafi, mwanakomana waKora, nehama dzake, ivo veimba yababa vake, vaKora, ndivo vaiva nebasa rokushumira, vakatarira masuo etabhenekari; madzibaba avo aitarira misasa yaJehovha, nokuchengeta mikova.
\v 20 Pinehasi mwanakomana waEriazari aiva murairi wavo kare, Jehovha akava naye.
\p
\v 21 Zekariya mwanakomana waMesheremia, akanga ari mutariri womukova wetende rokusangana.
\p
\v 22 Ava vose, vakatsaurwa kuti vave vatariri vamasuo, vakasvika mazana maviri negumi navaviri. Ava vose vakaverengwa mazita avo pamisha yavo, vakanga vakagadzwa pabasa ravo rakatarwa naDhavhidhi naSamueri muoni.
\p
\v 23 Naizvozvo ivo navana vavo vakanga vari vatariri vamasuo eimba yaJehovha, iyo imba yetabhenekari, vachiravana.
\p
\v 24 Vatariri vakanga vari kumativi mana, kumabvazuva, nokumavirira, nokumusoro, nenyasi.
\v 25 Hama dzavo pamisha yavo vaifanira kuuya nguva dzose kana mazuva manomwe apera, kuzogara navo.
\v 26 Nokuti vatariri vana vakuru vemikova, vakanga vari vaRevhi, vaiva pabasa iri rakatarwa, vaitarira makamuri nezvivigiro zvepfuma paimba yaMwari.
\v 27 Vaigarapo vakapoteredza imba yaMwari, nokuti ndivo vakanga vapiwa basa iri, vaiva nebasa rokuizarura mangwanani ose.
\v 28 Vamwe vavo vaifanira kutarira midziyo yokushumira nayo; nokuti yaipinzwa ichiverengwa, uye yaibudiswa ichiverengwa.
\v 29 Vamwe vavozve vakanga vakagadzwa kuti vatarire nhumbi nemidziyo yose nenzvimbo tsvene, noupfu hwakatsetseka, newaini, namafuta, nezvinonhuwira, nemiti inonhuwira.
\v 30 Vamwezve vavanakomana vavapristi vaifanira kugadzira zvinonhuwira zvakavenganiswa.
\v 31 Matitia, mumwe
\p wavakevhi, mwanakomana wedangwe waSharumi, wavaKora, wakanga akatarirwa basa rezvinhu zvaibikwa mugango.
\v 32 Navamwe vehama dzavo, vavana vaKora, vaifanira kutarira zvingwa zvokuratidza, kuzvigadzira Sabata rimwe nerimwe.
\p
\v 33 Uye ndivo vaimbi, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avaRevhi, vaigara mumakamuri vasingabati zvimwe; nokuti vaibata basa ravo masikati nousiku.
\p
\v 34 Ivo vaiva vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avaRevhi, vakuru kumarudzi avo; ndivo vaigara Jerusaremu.
\p
\v 35 Zvino paGibheoni pakanga pagere baba vaGibheoni, Jeyieri; zita romukadzi wake rakanga riri Maaka.
\v 36 Mwanakomana wake wedangwe waiva Abhidhoni, tevere Zuri, naKishi, naBhaari, naNeri, naNadhabhi;
\v 37 naGedhori, naAhio, naZekariya, naMikiroti.
\p
\v 38 Mikiroti wakabereka Shimeami. Ivo vaigarawo pamwechete nehama dzavo paJerusaremu, pakatarisana nehama dzavo.
\p
\v 39 Neri akabereka Kishi, Kishi akabereka Sauro, Sauro akabereka Jonatani, naMarikishua, naAbhinadhabhu, naEshibhaari.
\p
\v 40 Mwanakomana waJonatani waiva Meribhibhaari. Meribhibhaari akabereka Mika.
\v 41 Vanakomana vaMika: Pitoni, naMereki, naTarea, naAhazi.
\v 42 Ahazi akabereka Jara, Jara akabereka Arimeti naAzimavheti, naZimiri; Zimiri akabereka Moza;
\v 43 Moza akabereka Bhinea, naRefaya mwanakomana wake, naEreasa mwanakomana wake, naAzeri mwanakomana wake;
\v 44 Azeri akanga ana vanakomana vatanhatu; mazita avo ndiwo: Azirikami, naBhokeru, naIshimaeri, naShearia, naObhadhiya, naHanani. Ndivo vanakomana vaAzeri.
